Installation

Backend
Install dependencies:
bash
Copy code
pip install -r backend/requirements.txt
Run the backend server:
bash
Copy code
python backend/blockchain_security.py
Android
Open frontend/android in Android Studio.
Build and run the application.
iOS
Open frontend/ios/ParentaWatch.xcodeproj in Xcode.
Build and run the application on a simulator or connected device.
Web
Navigate to the frontend/web directory.
Open index.html in a browser to view the web interface.
Contributing

Pull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first to discuss the change you want to make.
